---
// src/components/ThreeWhys.astro
---
<section class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-white" style="width: 100%; margin: 0;">
  <div style="width: 100%; max-width: 80rem; margin: 0 auto; padding-left: 1rem; padding-right: 1rem;">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12 sm:mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 px-2" style="line-height: 1.5;">
        Job-site weather damage costs American builders <span class="text-[#0955A9]">$2.5 B each year</span>.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
        Warped lumber. Ruined adhesives. Delayed inspections. If it can melt, warp, or spoil, we climate-guard it.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Challenge/Solution Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-8 sm:mb-12">
      <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 px-2" style="line-height: 1.4;">
        Your Challenges. Our Solutions
      </h3>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
        From warped wood to workflow chaos, these climate-related problems blindside even the best-run projects, unless you stop them at the gate.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Three WHYs Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
      <!-- TIME -->
      <div class="text-center lg:col-span-1 sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-4 sm:mb-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 bg-[#0955A9] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <!-- Clock Icon from Heroicons -->
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4" style="line-height: 1.4;">TIME</h4>
        <ul class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 space-y-2 px-2">
          <li>Inconsistent site climate warps materials, driving up costs and blowing schedules.</li>
          <li>Damage triggers rework that pushes every trade's timeline back.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- MONEY -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-4 sm:mb-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 bg-[#0955A9] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <!-- Currency Dollar Icon from Heroicons -->
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4" style="line-height: 1.4;">MONEY</h4>
        <ul class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 space-y-2 px-2">
          <li>Climate-controlled units keep materials pristine, cutting pricey replacements.</li>
          <li>Mobile storage trims handling, warehousing, and damage expenses.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- LOGISTICS -->
      <div class="text-center sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-4 sm:mb-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 sm:w-16 sm:h-16 bg-[#0955A9] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <!-- Truck Icon from Heroicons -->
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 sm:w-8 sm:h-8 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </div>
        <h4 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3 sm:mb-4" style="line-height: 1.4;">LOGISTICS</h4>
        <ul class="text-sm sm:text-base text-gray-600 space-y-2 px-2">
          <li>Gooseneck trailers drop right on site, freeing workspace for all trades.</li>
          <li>No more costly shuttles from distant warehouses.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 